Summary: PHOTOGRAFING NIGHT SKY, IT WAS ON 3 OF MY PHOTOS, I WAS TAKING PICTURES OF THE SOUTHEAST, CAMERS WAS TIMED FOR 10 SECONDS WITH A 4 SECOND EXPOSURE, WITH A CANNON CAMERA
divs: Sighting DetailsTAKING PHOTOS AT 200AM WITH A CANNON CAMERA FACING THE SOUTHEAST, CAMERA SET FOR 10 SECONDS WITH A 4 SECOND EXPOSURE.........JUST WONDERING WHAT IT MIGHT BE, TRIPOD WAS NOT HIT OR MOVED, YOU CAN TELL BY THE BACKGROUD STARS THAT IT WAS IN FOCUS AND NOT MOVED, THESE SHOWED UP IN 3 FRAMES. I HAVE A SATALITE TRACKING ACROSS THE SKY AND A AIRPLANE, WAS NOT A LIGHTING BUG, IT WOULD HAVE BEEN WAY OUT OF FOCUS. JUST CAN,T IMAGINE WHAT IT COULD BE, WOULD BE GREAT, IF YOU COULD IDENTIFY THIS FOR ME. BECAUSE I AM CLUELESS AS TO WHAT IT COULD BE. WASN,T ANYTHING ON THE LENES, YOU CAN TELL IT WAS MOVING IN AN ODD WAY............THANKS JDS
